      "summary": "We are building a SaaS website where the Product is FlowJoe, and downloadable desktop app for Mac and Windows.  Our positioning in the market is anyone who sits between left and right brain thinking, where organization is a priority and connecting dots/threads/ideas is paramount to accomplishing their task. Examples would be: project or product managers, solo builders, small startups, and creatives.  FlowJoe is a new type of software that we are calling a \"Visual Intelligence Workspace\" because it gives the user a dynamic desktop-like surface from which to organize ideas, spread out documents and media, sort through information, take notes, and interact with AI, pulling content into their \"Flow\" and ultimately building a tree (or visual knowledge base) as a project grows.",
      "summaryUpdatedAt": 1781198586540,
